        </figure>

        <div class="monz-container">
          <div class="monz-grid">
            <div class="monz-col-3 mb-spacer-2">
              <h3>Critique by Andrea Lavagnini:</h3>
              <p>"'I imagined the imagination of the limit of imagination more or less limitless. But it turned out to be the opposite.' A psychotrance gallop in neurolinguistics, between psychedelic illustrations of Roscher’s monsters and laws of computer programming, between the aesthetic of David O’Reily and the psychoanalytic game, The Construction of ANSTALT3000 is the most ambitious, complex and incomprehensible animated short film that the public will have had the chance to see."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="monz-col-3">
              <div class="monz-tile break-inside-avoid-column mb-spacer-2">
                <button type="button" data-modal-target="modal-layout-columns-2-4" data-modal-toggle="modal-layout-columns-2-4" class="w-full text-left">
